f_k \in  BV(\mathbb{R^n}) \ 
n>1
f \in L^{1}_{\operatorname{loc}}(\mathbb{R^n})
 f_k \rightarrow f \ 
L^{1}_{\operatorname{loc}}(\mathbb{R^n}) \ 
 \|Df\|(\mathbb{R^n}) < \liminf \|Df_k\|(\mathbb{R^n})  \ 
\phi
f_k\to 0
L^1
|Df_k|
f_k(x)=k^{-1}\sin (kx_1) \phi(x) 
\int |\cos (kx_1)|\phi(x) \ge \int \cos^2 (kx_1)\phi(x)=\frac12\int \phi(x)+\frac12 \int \cos (2kx_1)\phi(x) 
\int \cos (2kx_1)\phi(x)  = - \frac{1}{2k} \int \sin (2kx_1)\frac{\partial \phi}{\partial x_1} \to 0 
